						</tr>";s:7:"toaddrs";s:46:"Karina Ricca &lt;karina@gprocommission.org&gt;";s:11:"description";s:11724:"<b id="sugar_text_gmail-docs-internal-guid-8af8084e-055b-8104-6b92-bfa100f2016f"></b><div style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;"><b><span style="font-weight:400;font-size:12pt;font-family:Arial;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;">Greetings on behalf of GProCommission, my name is </span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Arial;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;">Pastor German Ricca.</span><span style="font-weight:400;font-size:12pt;font-family:Arial;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;"> Regarding the t<u>wo-year GProCongress Anniversary</u>, I want to introduce GProCentral and many FREE Resources at the same time. I want to know if it is possible to start a follow-up regarding your Training Goals.</span></b></div><b></b><div style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;"><b><span style="font-weight:400;font-size:12pt;font-family:Arial;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;"><br /></span></b></div><b></b><div style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;"><b><span style="font-weight:400;font-size:12pt;font-family:Arial;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;">The GProCentral is a support team working to help pastoral trainers and pastoral leaders reach their ministry goals through connection to a global pastoral training network as well as to pastoral training resources and curriculum. You may visit our </span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Arial;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;"><a href="http://GProLearning.org">GProLearning.org</a></span><span style="font-weight:400;font-size:12pt;font-family:Arial;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;"> website to find many FREE resources or join our social media platform at </span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Arial;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;"><a href="http://GProConnext.com">GProConnext.com</a></span><span style="font-weight:400;font-size:12pt;font-family:Arial;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;">.</span></b></div><b></b><div style="font-weight:normal;line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;"><b><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Arial;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;"><br /></span></b></div><b></b><div style="font-weight:normal;line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;"><b><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Arial;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;">If you are involved in pastoral training we would like to connect with you further to build relationship if there are any ways we can serve you as well as to understand your objectives towards training pastors / pastoral leaders for the current year 2018.</span></b></div><b></b><div style="font-weight:normal;line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;"><b><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Arial;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;"><br /></span></b></div><b></b><div style="font-weight:normal;line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;"><b><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Arial;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;">Following the GProCongress for Pastoral Trainers in June 2016, the GProCommission seeks to capture in statistical form the number of pastors being trained around the world by various pastoral training organizations and institutions, churches, and individuals. The GProCommission acknowledges the immense work and effort you or any such organization have taken in training organizations and institutions, churches and individuals; which is a testimony of the great need to train pastoral leaders. The data collected is for statistical purposes only and would serve as a database for all who would want to know how many pastoral leaders have been trained, how many are being trained, and who is training them.</span></b></div><b></b><p dir="ltr" style="font-weight:normal;line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;"><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Arial;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;"> </span></p><div style="font-weight:normal;line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;"><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Arial;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;">We wish to record with recognition all you are doing to accelerate church health worldwide. We are eager to stand alongside you in your endeavor to honor your commitments. With that said, would you take a moment to answer a few questions here:</span></div><p dir="ltr" style="font-weight:normal;line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;"><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Arial;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;"> </span></p><br /><ul style="font-weight:normal;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type:disc;font-size:12pt;font-family:Arial;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;margin-left:11pt;"><div style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;"><span style="font-size:12pt;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;">What was the total (no of pastors/leaders) you had committed to train for the year 2018?</span></div></li><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type:disc;font-size:12pt;font-family:Arial;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;margin-left:11pt;"><div style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;"><span style="font-size:12pt;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;">What is the actual number of pastors/leaders you have trained? </span></div></li><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type:disc;font-size:12pt;font-family:Arial;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;margin-left:11pt;"><div style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;"><span style="font-size:12pt;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;">How do you think we could be of support in your training efforts? </span></div></li><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type:disc;font-size:12pt;font-family:Arial;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;margin-left:11pt;"><div style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;"><span style="font-size:12pt;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;">What kind of training (Topics) materials would you like us to support you with? </span></div></li></ul><p dir="ltr" style="font-weight:normal;line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;"><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Arial;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;"> </span></p><div style="font-weight:normal;line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;"><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Arial;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;">We encourage you to engage in this effort to strategically strengthen and multiply pastoral training efforts, yours and your ministry colleagues’ around the world. If you have had any specific issues in logging on to our website (listed above), please let us know. I would strongly encourage you to login today.</span></div><p dir="ltr" style="font-weight:normal;line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;"><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:Arial;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;"> </span></p><div style="font-weight:normal;line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;"><font color="#000000" face="Arial"><span style="font-size:16px;white-space:pre-wrap;">Please do not hesitate to contact me if you have any questions. Looking forward to hearing from you and thanks again for your interest in connecting with the GProCommission.</span></font></div><div style="font-weight:normal;line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;"><font color="#000000" face="Arial"><span style="font-size:16px;white-space:pre-wrap;"><br /></span></font></div><div style="font-weight:normal;line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;"><font color="#000000" face="Arial"><span style="font-size:16px;white-space:pre-wrap;">Have a blessed and peaceful day.</span></font></div><div style="font-weight:normal;line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;"><font color="#000000" face="Arial"><span style="font-size:16px;white-space:pre-wrap;"><br /></span></font></div><div>
